    <<SetMood "Takiko unknown">>
???: Cassie button up your shirt, Moron! *hmmp*  
      <<SetMood "Takiko hide">>
        <<SetMood "Cassie neutral">>
Cassie: You know I’m trying to, Takiko, but it won’t button.
      <<SetMood "Cassie hide">>
        <<SetMood "Takiko angry">>
Takiko: Can’t you buy decent clothes for once? 
Takiko: All you got is boobs for brains!
      <<SetMood "Takiko hide">>
        <<SetMood "Cassie happy">>
Cassie: Thank you! *smiles brightly*
      <<SetMood "Cassie hide">>
        <<SetMood "Takiko angry">>
Takiko: That was an insult pea brain.
Cassie looks hurt by Takiko’s comment, as they keep bickering back and forth, they see you standing to the side.
Takiko: Hey {$playerName}! Can you tell this pumpkin farmer to cover up!
You're suprised by the sudden attention.
      <<SetMood "Takiko hide">>
        <<SetMood "Cassie neutral">>
Cassie: *hmmp* Can you stop being wierd, {$playerName} tell her to back off!
Both girls turn to you waiting for your response.
    -> {$playerName}: (+ for Cassie) Takiko, relax. 
        <<jump D2_C_Positive1>>
    -> {$playerName}: (Neutral) Maybe we can all survive homeroom without declaring war? 
        <<jump D2_MC_Neutral1>>
    -> {$playerName}: (+ for Takiko) I mean... maybe buttoning it up would help.
        <<jump D2_T_Positive1>>
