title: D2_B_Corridor1
---
[Hallway] You see Bebe walking up to you.
      <<SetMood "Bebe neutral">>
Bebe: {$playerName}, wait a minute. 
You wait for her to walk up to you, she looks serious.
Bebe: I heard that Cassie and Takiko had an argument, do you know anything about it?
{$playerName}: They were bickering about Cassie's attire. 
      <<SetMood "Bebe angry">>
Bebe: *Ugh* Did you stand up for Cassie then?
<<if visited("D2_C_Positive1") or visited("D2_MC_Neutral1")>>
{$playerName}: I told Takiko to leave her alone. 
      <<SetMood "Bebe neutral">>
Bebe: Good, Takiko always had a brick up her ass. Where is your next lesson?
{$playerName}: In the library.
Bebe walks you to your study period while telling stories about her's and Cassie's friendship.
      <<SetMood "Bebe hide">>
<<else>>
{$playerName}: No, I told Cassie that her clothes are not appropriate for school. 
Bebe: Who are you to tell a girl what she should wear, you moron?!
      <<SetMood "Bebe hide">>
Bebe storms away. You walk to the library confused. 
<<endif>>
As you enter the library you see Emiko sitting in a dark corner.
You also see Nancy, she's sitting in a cozy corner on the other side of the room.
Who do you join?
    -> Emiko
        <<jump D2_E_Library1>>
    -> Nancy
        <<jump D2_N_Library1>>
