title: D2_E_Library1
---
You walk to the corner where Emiko sits. 
{$playerName}: What are you doing here?
      <<SetMood "Emiko angry">>
Emiko: Reading, can't you see that?
{$playerName}: I meant, why are you in a corner, did you get punished?
Emiko: No, it's my favorite place, it's dark, warm, and no one bothers me. 
{$playerName}: Should I leave?
Emiko: No, you can stay. 
{$playerName}: Do you want to study together?
Emiko: No, I prefer to read my book. 
    ->(+ for Emiko) The Bell Jar. I never read that book but I heard it’s good. Can I read with you? 
        {$playerName}: The Bell Jar. I never read that book but I heard it’s good. Can I read with you?       
              <<SetMood "Emiko neutral">>     
        You can see a little smile creep on her face. 
        Emiko : Of course, I didn’t think we would vibe like that. *smiles*
        She scoots to the side, you sit beside her as Emiko gives you an earbud.
              <<SetMood "Emiko hide">>
    ->(- for Emiko) Don’t we have a study period right now? You should be studying. 
        {$playerName}: Don’t we have a study period right now? You should be studying.
        Emiko: Why would I, it's not like I care?!
        She looks visibly upset. 
        {$playerName}: Shouldn't you care about your future?
        Emiko: You don't understand, I wont have one. 
              <<SetMood "Emiko hide">>
        Emiko storms off upset. 
        {$playerName}: *What's that supposed to mean?*

